description: Legendary jazz musician Branford Marsalis is bringing his talent to western Oregon. This week, he's performing with the Eugene Symphony. You can catch him at the Hult Center on Jan. 22 and 8 p.m.
title: Interview: Saxophonist Branford Marsalis
